ul.li:
Document context menu of current editor XML Refactoring Surround with tag... (Ctrl+E) (Alt+Shift+E) ( (Cmd+Alt+E on Mac OS)) - Allows you to choose a tag that encloses a selected portion of content. If there is no selection, the start and end tags are inserted at the caret position. The caret is placed:
between the start and end tag, if the Cursor position between tags option is set;
at the end of the start tag, in an insert-attribute position, if the Cursor position between tags option is not set.
